</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="band sc-7464c750-0 dnYSzV details-parent pb-5-parent" id="page13633-band534132"><div class="container details pb-5"><div id="layout-534132" class="sc-f8c8761-0 kSicyH layout row d-flex"><div class="d-flex flex-column col-md-8 align-items-start justify-content-start sc-49cdea-0"><div class="sc-648810d1-0 cqRlRw text rich-text w-100 w-100" data-isrtl="false" id="page13633-band534132-Text534133"><div class="text-center"><p class="text-left">Guy Ritchie directs an all-star cast in this comedy crime filled with fast-paced dialogue, choreographed fights and lots of action, and humor where a multimillionaire real estate scam catches the eye of every gangster in London.</p></div></div><div class="sc-648810d1-0 cqRlRw text rich-text w-100 w-100" data-isrtl="false" id="page13633-band534132-Text534134"><div><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Starring:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">Gerard Butler, Tom Wilkinson, Thandiwe Newton, Mark Strong, Idris Elba, Tom Hardy, Toby Kebbell, Jeremy Piven, Chris "Ludacris" Bridges</p><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Directors:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">Guy Ritchie</p><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Writers:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">Guy Ritchie</p><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Producers:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">Joel Silver, Susan Downey, Steve Clark-Hall, Guy Ritchie, Steve Richards, Navid McIlhargey</p></div></div></div><div class="d-flex flex-column col-md-4 align-items-start justify-content-start sc-49cdea-0"><div class="sc-648810d1-0 cqRlRw text rich-text w-100 w-100" data-isrtl="false" id="page13633-band534132-Text534135"><div class="text-center"><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Genres:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">Action, Crime, High Octane Thrillers, Organised Crime, Big Screen Crime</p></div></div><div class="sc-648810d1-0 cqRlRw text rich-text w-100 w-100" data-isrtl="false" id="page13633-band534132-Text534136"><div class="text-center"><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Release Year:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">2008</p></div></div><div class="sc-648810d1-0 cqRlRw text rich-text w-100 w-100" data-isrtl="false" id="page13633-band534132-Text534137"><div><h3 class="text-left"><strong>Rating:&nbsp;</strong></h3><p class="text-left">16+&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="band sc-7464c750-0 dnYSzV -parent" id="page13633-band534144"><div class="my-5 container"><div id="layout-534144" class="sc-f8c8761-0 kSicyH layout row d-flex"><div class="d-flex flex-column col-md-12 align-items-start justify-content-start sc-49cdea-0"><div id="page13633-band534144-Code534145" class="rich-text"><div id="plan-picker"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="band sc-7464c750-0 ksHxvr pt-3-parent pb-5-parent max-section-all-here-ribbon-parent" id="page13633-band534163"><div class="my-5 container pt-3 pb-5 max-section-all-here-ribbon"><div id="layout-534163" class="sc-f8c8761-0 kSicyH layout row d-flex"><div class="d-flex flex-column col-md-12 align-items-center justify-content-center sc-49cdea-0"><div class="sc-648810d1-0 cqRlRw text rich-text w-100 w-100" data-isrtl="false" id="page13633-band534163-Text534164"><div class="text-center"><h2>Find Iconic Entertainment for Every Mood</h2></div></div><a aria-label="" class="sc-96624f99-1 hqHyXl btn px-4 btn--secondary btn-md" data-align="center" href="/" id="page13633-band534163-Button534165" rel="noopener" role="link" target="_top"><span class="sc-96624f99-0 kNRKqa styled-button-text" data-show-play-icon="false">Home</span></a></div></div></div></section><section class="band sc-7464c750-0 dnYSzV lang-selector-parent" id="page13633-band534172"><div class="py-3 container lang-selector"><div id="layout-534172" class="sc-f8c8761-0 kSicyH layout row d-flex"><div class="d-flex flex-column col-md-12 align-items-center justify-content-center sc-49cdea-0"></div></div></div></section><section class="band sc-7464c750-0 dnYSzV ma