3csmall\u003e*Sports add-on price only. Base plan subscription from £5.99/month also required. Auto-renews unless add-on or base plan cancelled. Contains ads and may contain sponsorship and Cross-Promotional Content. T\u0026Cs apply. 18+.\u003c/small\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\\r\\n      \u003c/div\u003e\\r\\n    \u003c/div\u003e\\r\\n  \u003c/div\u003e\\r\\n\u003c/div\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"type\":\"string\",\"cmsType\":\"textarea\",\"mappingId\":\"idref76\"},{\"value\":\"{\\\"legal\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"This service is provided by Discovery Communications Benelux B.V. Contact us at Chiswick Park Building 2, 566 Chiswick High Road, London, W4 5YB or support.uk@hbomax.com. ©2026 Discovery Communications Benelux B.V. HBO Max is property of Home Box Office, Inc. TNT Sports is used under license. All rights reserved.\\\"},\\\"secondaryRow\\\":[{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Accessibility\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.wbd.com/accessibility-statement/\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Privacy Policy\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/privacy\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Children's Privacy Policy\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/privacy/children\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Terms of Use\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/terms-of-use\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Manage Cookies\\\"},\\\"isCCPALink\\\":true},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Corporate Infomation\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/corp-info\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Modern Slavery Agreement\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://static-wbd-cdn.wbd.com/s3_assets/docs/2025-07/global_msa_statement_2024.pdf\\\",\\\"openInNewTab\\\":true},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Help Center\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://help.hbomax.com/\\\",\\\"openInNewTab\\\":true}],\\\"primaryRow\\\":[{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Explore What’s On\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/gb/en/sitemap\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Shows\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/gb/en/shows\\\"},{\\\"label\\\":{\\\"en_US\\\":\\\"Movies\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"/gb/en/movies\\\